title: War of the Roses: Dave Pulls an Audible on the Guy
description: Amanda has a child with her fiance, David, and their kid told her something weird about David and his friend Vicki that is leading her to believe David has something going on with Vicki.  Dave pulls a switch-a-roo to try to catch David in a lie, did he fall for it?
